sub_title: Project Management | Logistics and Supply Chain
summary:
Import specialist with over 10 years of working experience looking for new role as Project Manager in a field related to digital products. Express strong interest to work in an innovative environment where people implement unconventional ideas and open to everything new.
- expertise in Russian and Eurasian Customs Union (EACU) legislation
- experience in importing of equipment, clothes, petroleum products from China and EU to Russia
- strong analytical and organisational skills
